{"id":186292,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/印度推出35美元7英寸android平板/","date":"2011-10-06T01:30:04Z","modified":"2011-10-06T01:30:04Z","title":"印度推出35美元7英寸Android平板","content":"<p>路透社报导，印度宣布了世界最廉价的平板电脑——35美元7寸Android平板Aakash，运行Android 2.2 (Froyo)，显示屏支持触控，重350克，内存256MB，支持WiFi。平板由英国公司DataWind开发，将在印度组装。平板电脑主要提供给学生使用，印度政府计划在大规模推广前进行小范围试验。印度电信和教育部部长Kapil Sibal表示，不久以后每个学校的学生都将有一部35美元电脑，它将帮助学生提高学习质量。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/190e93a8/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA35%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%837%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8Android%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fhardware.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F05%2F1135248%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA35%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%837%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8Android%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fhardware.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F05%2F1135248%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/114252877072/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/190e93a8/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/114252877072/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/190e93a8/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=LIlGhnwqu0M:hjeGLkpLub8:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=LIlGhnwqu0M:hjeGLkpLub8:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场